_sText:
This is my first map, be kind!

___________
fy_poolcamp_vTiny

I'm the only one who have edited on this map.
___________
You might also want these:

-|mp_limitteams 20 (To make it possible to have 20 persons on a map)
-|mp_autoteambalance 0 (0 = NO TeamBalance: OFF | 1 = Auto TeamBalance: ON)
___________
This map has HDR, so when you open it, it might look weird - If this happens, type "buildcubemaps" in console. A little cutscene will pop up, after that, exit the server and CS:S. After that, you open it again and it should work.

EDIT: I went on a LAN and some of the people that were there downloaded this map, typed "buildcubemaps", but when they made a server out of it, others couldn't join. If you don't know how to fix this, don't type in the code, because it works without it.
___________
PM if it's a bug, or you wanted to ask about something.

2012 edit; This was made for some large LAN I was attending to, I also made it because PoolParty was my favorite map and I thought map-making was cool. It was just for fun :)
